Carlos Tevez has told Juventus he wants to leave the club this summer . 
  The striker wants to return to his first club Boca Juniors in Argentina . 
  Boca have confirmed they are close to completing a deal for the striker . 
  Tevez must terminate his contract with Juventus before he can leave . 
  The 31-year-old's deal with Juventus expires at the end of next season . 
 